						Information Systems Strategy and IT Governance
				(තොරතුරු පද්ධති සාර්ථකව භාවිතා කරනා ක්‍රමවේදය සහ  තොරතුරු තාක්ෂණ පරිපාලනය)
											

April 2024
	Question 1)
		A. State four (4) symptoms of poor IT alignment. 													[4 Marks]  [OK]
		B. Define IT maturity. 																				[3 Marks]  [OK]
		C. Explain the stages of IT maturity and the characteristics associated with each stage. 			[6 Marks]  [OK]
		D. Discuss the evolution of IT functions in an organisation with the help of a diagram. 			[6 Marks]  [OK]
		E. Assess the impact of the external environment on the implementation of IT governance strategies. [6 Marks]  [OK]


