	Question 1)


		A. Differentiate IT management and IT governance. 												[4 Marks] [ok]
		
		B. Examine the dissimilarities between "IT service managernent" and "IT governance" in  
		   relation to the maturity of an organisation's IT function.									[6 Marks] [OK]

 		C. Describe the process of IT governance with the help of a neat diagram. 						[10 Marks] [ok] 

